<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1264,561,585]" box="[151,1264,561,585]" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,561,585]" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">FIGURE 1</emphasis>
. Dorsal (A) and ventral (B) views of holotype of 
<emphasis box="[804,1059,562,585]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">
<taxonomicName box="[804,971,562,585]" class="Reptilia" family="Gymnophthalmidae" genus="Petracola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="waka" status="sp. nov.">Petracola waka</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[978,1059,562,585]" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
Line equals 1 mm.
